queries.sql: SELECT `t_coin_request`.*, `b`.`phone` as `buyer_phone`, `b`.`name` as `buyer_name`, `s`.`phone` as `seller_phone`, `s`.`name` as `seller_name` FROM `t_coin_request` LEFT JOIN `users` `b` ON `b`.`id` = `t_coin_request`.`buyer_id` LEFT JOIN `users` `s` ON `s`.`id` = `t_coin_request`.`seller_id` WHERE DATE(t_coin_request.created_at) >= '2025-12-02' AND DATE(t_coin_request.created_at) <= '2025-12-02' ORDER BY `t_coin_request`.`id` DESC LIMIT 20
